title: Helena Paparizou - Vrisko To Logo Na Zo (2008)

Helena Paparizou - Vrisko To Logo Na Zo
MP3 | CBR 128Kbps 44100 Stereo | 49:20 | 45 MB

"Vrisko To Logo Na Zo" (I Find The Reason To Live) is the third studio album by the Greek singer-songwriter Helena Paparizou which was released in Greece on May 29, 2008 by Sony BMG. Its the first time that Niclas Olausson and Toni Mavridis have produced the entire album and that Paparizou has penned several tracks for. It is also the first time that a duet is included on one of her solo albums.
